{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                 // hydrogen // schema // engineering"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Engineering pillar — Complete CAD/Blueprint drawing primitives."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Overview"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | The Engineering pillar provides all primitives needed to create"},{"LineComment":" | technical drawings, blueprints, and CAD documentation:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Tolerance**: GD&T symbols, tolerances, datum references"},{"LineComment":" | - **Dimension**: Dimension lines, arrowheads, text formatting"},{"LineComment":" | - **Section**: Cut planes, hatching patterns, section views"},{"LineComment":" | - **Drawing**: Sheet sizes, title blocks, scales, views"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Why Engineering Matters"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | At billion-agent scale, engineering primitives enable:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **Manufacturing**: Direct machine-readable specifications"},{"LineComment":" | - **Inspection**: Automated quality control criteria"},{"LineComment":" | - **Documentation**: Standardized technical drawings"},{"LineComment":" | - **Collaboration**: Interoperable CAD data exchange"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Standards Supported"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **ASME Y14.5-2018**: GD&T (US standard)"},{"LineComment":" | - **ISO 1101:2017**: Geometric tolerancing (international)"},{"LineComment":" | - **ISO 128/129**: Technical drawings"},{"LineComment":" | - **ISO 5457/7200**: Sheet sizes and title blocks"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Submodules"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - `Engineering.Tolerance`: GD&T, tolerances, surface finish"},{"LineCommen